{"tid":684593,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇工係星期六日先返?","createTime":"2018-05-30T16:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T17:31:47.000Z","uid":98452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"92259e8e6c2b43689cfe2ea2a0eab7ecdc221096","tid":684593,"uid":98452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"返緊一般Office工, 但係星期六日好得閒 (唔會有fd約我去玩, 更加冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n諗緊不如揾多份Part time打發時間又有錢收<br />\n<br />\n上網揾兼職好多都起碼要一星期返三日以上<br />\n同埋我自己唔太想做飲食業/Sales<br />\n想問下會唔會有星期六日先返既工 (六/日/兩日 都OK)<br />\n我知自己好多要求<br />\n<br />\n但真心想問有冇呢啲Part Time? 同埋應該喺邊到揾工?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8f925a8b88705e31ba499edc7e24141f56adc0","tid":684593,"uid":27370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"老救"},{"pid":"252c81952b3484740fc4080686c043fd5bb7ed4f","tid":684593,"uid":98452,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"9c8f925a8b88705e31ba499edc7e24141f56adc0","tid":684593,"uid":27370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"老救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"我聽日開始學游水既話幾耐可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad70b389cc4da7a217571e4c44d64911ac8b287f","tid":684593,"uid":27370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"勤力嘅話由0到學識我諗至少起碼半年"},{"pid":"87bc568992cc3da05fe0305e9200d1a8271b063b","tid":684593,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"馬會"},{"pid":"f8ee24bc6f176551c966fc441f06f33fe32e3fc9","tid":684593,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88f56fc